cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper proposes novel data augmentation techniques for deep reinforcement learning (DRL) in robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also focuses on improving the efficiency of observed interaction, which suggests a connection to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the proposed techniques involve transformations of trajectories, which could be related to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions goal definitions, which could be related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves reinforcement learning, which could be related to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
